content: <@1269412506699431997> hello, welcome! Are you interested in joining our Text team? We have onboarding trainings.

You aren't missing anything right now though as there aren't any active campaigns right now. While waiting, consider joining a phone bank or another opportunity!

<@1277645699105816750>  to get a head start please add first and last name on Discord Display name. Soon a Greeter will message you on Discord Direct Messages, please check your DM area (game controller bubble, top left corner of screen).

<@1277645699105816750>  To change your Discord Display Name, visit your profile bottom left corner of screen, select the gear icon 'User Settings' -> edit profile name. 'edit display name'
